Package: BRREWABC
Type: Package
Title: Batched Resilient and Rapid Estimation Workflow through Approximate Bayesian Computation
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Gaël Beaunée <gael.beaunee@inrae.fr>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Gaël", "Beaunée", , email = "gael.beaunee@inrae.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0002-2627", Website = "https://gaelbn.com"))
  )
Description: An R package designed to facilitate inference through a parallelized
    Approximate Bayesian Computation Sequential Monte Carlo (ABC SMC) algorithm.
    This package streamlines the process of conducting Bayesian inference for
    complex models by implementing efficient parallelization techniques.
